<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV20">
<l>kūcamoṉṟu miṉṟimācu ṇampaṭuttu vēlainīr,</l>
<l>pēcaniṉṟa tēvarvantu pāṭamuṉki ṭantatum</l>
<l>pācaniṉṟa nīrilvāḻu māmaiyāṉa kēcavā</l>
<l>ēcavaṉṟu nīkiṭanta vāṟukūṟu tēṟavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You previously reclined on the ocean water spreading out a serpent,</l>
<l rend="indent">without any inhibitions,</l>
<l>as the gods—who stand [for others] to praise [them]— came and sang [about You];</l>
<l>You lay down the other day in such a way that [people] insult [You saying],</l>
<l>‘O Keśava who became a tortoise that lovingly lives in the water!’</l>
<l rend="indent">Tell [me about these] so that [I am] enlightened!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
